1. I want the robot to organize books.
2. I want the robot to help lend and return books without the need for human librarians,
   or the need for the borrower to find the book physically.
3. I want the robot to help the customer find the book he/she needs through the name of the author or genre,
   and for the robot to specify the versions of the book available currently.
4. I want the robot to clean the books.
